modName: A simple save out of helgen
summary: A simple save game out of Helgen. Nord, male Mikey in Riverwood. For more read description.
descriptionHtml:
2nd Mod

For those who do not wish to start off in Helgen. You are now in Riverwood.
The player has the following items.
Imperial armor
imperial boots
imperial bracers
imperial officers helmet
iron shield
imperial sword
longbow
24 iron arrows

{Description}
For those who do not wish to start off in Helgen.
You are a level 1 Nord, Male Mikey. (if you do not like this then open up the console and type \"Showracemenu\" (without quotes) and you will be able to change your character to your desires.

{Installation}
1)open with winrar(or whatever software you may use)
2) Extract to desktop
3)open your Documents/My games/Skyrim/ Saves folder 
4) Click and drag or copy and paste or cut and paste the file into your saves directory
YOUR DONE!! :D ENJOY!!
author: Maykelhd1998
